OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start with sunny spells.
OL,6,FAny cloud gradually breaking up
OL,7,Fthrough the day to give largely clear
OL,8,Fskies and plenty of sunshine in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Very warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry evening with largely
OL,12,Fclear skies and evening sunshine to
OL,13,Fstart but turning cloudier. Dry and
OL,14,Fmostly cloudy overnight with clear
OL,15,Fintervals in the west.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,18,Fvariable cloud but still plenty of
OL,19,Flong sunny spells. Feeling very warm
OL,20,Fin the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
